Class Tracker

java.lang.Object
  Tracker

public class Tracker
extends java.lang.Object

Tracker class is a used to model the tracker. It has only one main function which is connect the client can connect to the tracker and send a message to it. Get the trackers response and do what it needs to do with it.

Author:
Harshil Shah, Ted Nohh
